author: Lobo_da_boss_
title: Ok figure
review:
Opening -

This variant of Luke Skywalker is based of one of or his most iconic outfit from episode four .

Minifigures-

The figure has a nice light tan hair piece , a useful head print and some continuous printing from torso to legs . The accessory is a standard blue bladed lightsaber .

In conclusion-

he is an ok figure who is fairly common but if you want it get it .
